content:
# I successfully harvested 5 stones, and my inventory now contains the necessary materials to craft a stone furnace.
# 
# Next, I will craft the stone furnace, which will allow me to smelt iron ore into iron plates.

# First, I need to ensure that I have enough iron ore to craft the iron plates and the iron gear wheel required for the burner mining drill.
# I will now gather some iron ore again since I need more than what I initially attempted to harvest.

# Let's move back to the iron ore patch and gather 10 iron ore this time.
move_to(Position(x=-16.0, y=26.0))  # Moving back to the iron ore patch's center
harvest_resource(Position(x=-16.0, y=26.0), quantity=10)  # Attempting to harvest 10 iron ore again.
